messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

Pray for me I was in a abusive relationship for last 17 years and I decided to leave. Then I vowed to be pure but I got into the spirit of lust recently though Facebook I started  chatting with men. Later I felt dirty. Am 47 years and a mother of thee children please pray for me to get a husband am lonely

I'm truly sorry to hear about your struggles. We are here to pray with you and for you. 

Heavenly Father, we come before you today, lifting up this brave individual who has faced so much. We ask for your healing and strength as they navigate this new chapter in their life. Please help them to find purity and satisfaction in You, and guide them away from the spirit of lust. We pray for companionship and a loving husband to come into their life, bringing joy and support. Fill their heart with peace and remind them of Your steadfast love. In Jesus' name, we pray. Amen.

If you need further support or resources, feel free to reach out!
